body.description: First Aid Only's 25-person Logger's First Aid Kit prepares you for tackling emergencies on a jobsite. This 69-piece compact first aid kit has supplies for treating cuts, scrapes, and wounds. Kit contains 16 each 3-inches length by 1-inches width adhesive strips, 2 each 9-inches length by 5-inches width large wound compress, 10 each 4-inches length by 4-inches width gauze pads, 2 each 40-inches Triangular Bandage, 2 each 5 yards length by 2-inches width stretch gauze bandage, 12 each antihistamine capsules, 1 each CPR face shield/one way valve, 10 each benzalkonium chloride antiseptic towelettes, 2 each aluminized thermal blankets, 1 each rubber tourniquet, 1 each wire splint, 1 each 5 yards length by 1/2-inches width adhesive tape, 2 each 5 yards length by 2-inches width elastic bandage, 1 pair latex examination gloves, 1 each metal scissors, 1 each plastic forceps, 1 each notepad w/CPR instructions, 1 each pencil, 1 each first aid instruction booklet. This small first aid kit comes in an easy-to-carry metal case with easy-to-release latches designed to ensure quick first aid access in the event of an emergency. Case measures 6-1/2-inches length by 9-1/2-inches width by 2-3/4-inches height. Our first aid kits for businesses, jobsites, and construction vehicles allow you to treat minor cuts and scrapes just about anywhere.
